{"tid":1428280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 唔好娛樂化膠化差佬記招","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:37:44.000Z","uid":35637,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"71e57974b0a24b9beb805ed32dc37cd22e003762","tid":1428280,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"要嚴肅看待<br />\n認真回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整條片 作歌 改圖黎笑個呀sir對大局冇幫助<br />\n甚至乎增加歪理曝光率"},{"pid":"f7e58e09e256535f5f00455ffe4300d246da6bbf","tid":1428280,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"唔好膠化件事"},{"pid":"edee6a66a60360758cc83c6df77dc13813604832","tid":1428280,"uid":81628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"認同，同埋唔好比憤怒遮蓋左理智<br />\n最佳方法係唸點樣反駁佢地，證明佢地係到顛倒是非"},{"pid":"c3c80f7f0baa845aef6cae60491cddd79ddd07fe","tid":1428280,"uid":39682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"同意，we are at war<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5927afb1e8fecccaf9d6220844755f2d79732c","tid":1428280,"uid":55351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"打撚死對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好輕敵"},{"pid":"984ce31764372301b4e0afacd88467bb32010dd1","tid":1428280,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c915c74f00f42dd5b2d23bf3dd43bb549adfcfd","tid":1428280,"uid":292131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"今日見到噤多人係度玩<br />\n諗起14年膠化黑狗記招<br />\n跟住個記招開始談笑風生<br />\n最後？<br />\n<br />\n今日睇到天水圍保釋嘅市民比狗撚到去上水<br />\n嬲撚到仆街<br />\n再見到大家噤開心玩鐳射筆<br />\n真係想又嬲又想喊<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1428748/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1428748/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c3aa96dbcf7cd87f3e093521e14a8f2d0d4a2cc3","tid":1428280,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1c7205412a559ebee57212c45f8263eeada89c60","tid":1428280,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"專心做自己文宣，放映會，連儂牆，行動<br />\n唔好被帶風向，黑警同港共記者會對象唔係我地<br />\n堅持五大訴求"},{"pid":"a8b0fec6f9a0e0d451d8116cbe6915c4b0bc636a","tid":1428280,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7205412a559ebee57212c45f8263eeada89c60","tid":1428280,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"專心做自己文宣，放映會，連儂牆，行動<br />\n唔好被帶風向，黑警同港共記者會對象唔係我地<br />\n堅持五大訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f25dfcb3ad06451677b284eb066ccae79fb59a","tid":1428280,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"305cb511bc6eeddd2081b9a950c65e7d32ca833c","tid":1428280,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0882a99de19f5ff7294d4f2fd27a2b80ec8a778c","tid":1428280,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"推撚到每個人都睇到"},{"pid":"a1c3cd14d05f94213b5663a03cc02a5b3a2310e3","tid":1428280,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:44:45.000Z","msg":"後現代雨傘模式已經出現 考驗香港人智慧一關又黎喇 <br />\n我地要突破昔日困局<br />\n<br />\n支持連仔整預設回覆係不推文， 當大家想推某一個ＰＯＳＴ 先要ＣＬｉｃｋ 我要推Ｐｏｓｔ <br />\n仲要 限次數 <br />\n<br />\n一禁熱門 睇留言就ＣＨＥＣＫ到邊Ｄ係５毛ＡＣ係到帶風向 <br />\n總之 不分化不割席 不要大台 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436142/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436142/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cd77bb505a8ec491784853e05459b35e46e4683d","tid":1428280,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"雨傘時既4點鐘許Sir就係咁"},{"pid":"f7476d88efcbb55fda2d031f967792b900fdfa08","tid":1428280,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"其實點解狗狗記者會我地咁驚呢<br />\n我覺得係CCTVB加日日開，瘋狂Cut黎Cut去，去洗腦<br />\n好容易令人成日focus左過去<br />\n不過而家記者咁強勢都叫好啲，仲有民間記者會幫手反駁<br />\n<br />\n但係而家因為已經唔係14年，唔係日日佔領<br />\n佢日日都唔一定有野講，所以而家瘋狂做埋啲鳩屎野<br />\n引哂你地啲人出黎，咁先有野講<br />\n<br />\n應對：<br />\n其實我覺得最好就係冷處理佢，當佢冇到<br />\n不過大前提係CCTVB要執粒先<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要加強抵制CCTVB，加強文宣<br />\n要改變文宣策略，要學下英國脫歐嗰套電影<br />\n其實都好多Post都有講過，不過再講下"},{"pid":"1885c1a49fad84dddce0e0853b48f3895b9a00a3","tid":1428280,"uid":284592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"無錯，革命唔係請客食飯！<br />\n玩一陣可以，膠化就死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dedcbaa24b3241cea649d9b3b37d01d31a7d9f1","tid":1428280,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"佔中許sir既教訓大家要好好記住。"},{"pid":"20a3ded3a4b89715f73f608a545b0d3959d1219f","tid":1428280,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"推撚到每個人都睇到"},{"pid":"0cb81e8adc8810995446dc2b083a1c5963692898","tid":1428280,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"日日掟PPRB出黎獻醜 做小丑<br />\n記招柒晒都唔駛負責任<br />\n政府